Last day to register for #TheWorldsBestJob. 
Applied yet?

There’s a seat open in the Harley-Davidson Business Unit Brand Marketing Team at Hero MotoCorp.

If you eat, sleep, breathe and preach all things motorcycle, tell us why you deserve this seat in a post, video or reel and tag #theworldsbestjob, @harleydavidson_india and @powerdrift.

Age no bar. Prior experience no bar. Gender no bar.

Perks include a riding adventure to the Himalayas each year on the Pan America 1250, participation in the BIG 5 H.O.G. Rallies, a crash course at the Harley-Davidson University, full H-D riding gear, the privilege of managing the Harley-Davidson Brand in India, and - the best perk of all - your very own Harley-Davidson Nightster.

Applications close on May 21 at 11.59 pm.

*Conditions apply
Something’s coming up and we thought you guys should know! More on this soon #theworldsbestjob
